Package camp

Class Camp

  • Object
    • Camp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class Camp
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a Camp created in the system. A camp contains information related to the camp such as remaining slots left, Camp Name, Staff in Charge.
    Since:
    2023-11-17
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Soo Qi Yang, Teo Kai Xuan, Masagca Merwyn Louie Dumasis, Nguyen Phuong Linh, Tee Jeeng Yee
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
